item.title: Cant Tele On Phonescape ? Lil' Help?
item.dc:creator: @Khasck Khasck
item.description:
@Khasck wrote:

are you in lvl 20+ wildy? lol
make sure your in a safe zone, like the varrock dummy training shop.
then try to teleport on all the spells
if none of them work, then you screwed over you coding, becuase ive worked with phonescape before, and ive never gotten this problem.
but to fix it, open up client.java and search for “you cannot teleport above 20 wilderness”
and sift through it, untill you see “varrock teleport” or “spell ##” and above it, then make sure it says “you cannnot teleport above 20 wilderness” below it, and then look for a void or a cancelation in the coding, and take it out, along with the message.
hope this helps ya,

-Will
